                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Tell all the Truth but tell it slant --</l>
                    <l>Success in Circuit lies</l>
                    <l>Too <app type="revision"><lem>bold</lem><rdg>bold</rdg></app>
bright for our infirm Delight</l>
                    <l>The Truth's superb surprise</l>
                    <l>As Lightning to the Children eased</l>
                    <l>With explanation kind</l>
                    <l>The Truth must dazzle <app type="revision"><lem>moderately</lem><rdg>moderately</rdg></app>
gradually</l>
                    <l>Or every man be blind --</l>
                </lg>
